headline: State regulators grant time for FPL and key stakeholders to finalize settlement that keeps customer bills well below national average
summary: State regulators unanimously agreed today to give Florida Power & Light Company and key stakeholder groups time to finalize a comprehensive four-year rate settlement that would keep customer bills well below the national average through the end of the decade.
